#Text=Wikinews interviews Australian disability standing skier Jonty O'Callaghan
#Text=Monday , December 17 , 2012
#Text=Wikinews reporter
#Text=LauraHale interviews Australian Paralympic skier Jonty O'Callaghan
#Text=Recently , Wikinews spent time with with Australian Paralympic skier Jonty O'Clallaghan who was in Copper Mountain , Colorado for the IPC Nor-Am Cup .
#Text=( ( Wikinews ) )
#Text=I 'm interviewing Jonty O'Callaghan , one of the Australian skiers with the IPC [ International Paralympic Committee ]
#Text=Nor-Am Cup , and you 're a fifteen-year-old ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : Yup .
#Text=Yeah , I 've been skiing since I was about ten and I really enjoy racing .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) I talked to your father , he said you 're kind of thinking Sochi ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan :
#Text=It 's the matter of if I qualify by getting enough good races and points .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) How do you balance skiing with doing school ?

#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : Over the past few years in Australia I 've been doing full time in tenth grade in the Australian winter , which means the school at the mountain brings up my work from my home school in Melbourne to do up at the mountain when I 'm not skiing .
#Text=( ( WN ) )
#Text=Since you 're not on the development team , do you get enough support or your parents are supporting this ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : Yeah , my parents support me all the way .
#Text=I 've never doubted their support always though the journeys and I [ thank them ] for their support throughout and continuing through my journeys .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) What classification are you ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : I am LW9-1 .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) What does that mean for people who know nothing about classification ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : I basically have a disability on the right side of my body .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Yep .
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : which weakens two of my limbs and which means I favor my left side a lot more .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Did you have that from birth ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : Yeah , it was caused by premature birth .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Do you do any other sports anything other than skiing or are you one of those Australian ski bunnies ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : I 've done a lot of sports doing my journey , I 've always played cricket , Australian football , played a little tennis , and I like golf too as a hobby .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Are you going to and be one of those dual Paralympians for Winter and Summer ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : No , because I do n't think any other sports
#Text=I like are in the Summer Olympics .
#Text=I think I 'll pursue them after I finished my skiing career , because cricket you can do when you 're much older .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Is there anything else people should know about you ?
#Text=Jonty O'Callaghan : Yeah , I 'm just looking forward to the future and hoping for the best and maybe some medals .
#Text=( ( WN ) ) Okay cool , thank you very much .
